      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "activated",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A Boolean value indicating whether spring-loading has been activated on the destination. "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " indicates that spring-loading has been activated. "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " indicates that spring-loading has been deactivated."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "draggingInfo",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "An "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "NSDraggingInfo"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " object, which provides information about the drag event, including the dragged data."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Typically, spring-loading is fully activated when a hover timeout occurs or the user finishes force clicking on a destination object to initiate spring-loading. In these cases, the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "springLoadingActivated:draggingInfo:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method is only called once with an "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "activated"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " parameter value of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "However, if the destination is configured with continuous activation ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSSpringLoadingOptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " was set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSSpringLoadingContinuousActivation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), then the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "springLoadingActivated:draggingInfo:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method is called twice. First, it’s called with an "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "activated"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " parameter value of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when a hover timeout occurs or the user begins force clicking on a destination object to initiate spring-loading. Then, it’s called again with an "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "activated"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " parameter value of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when the hover exits the destination’s bounds or the user finishes force clicking on the destination object."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
